[{"type":"3","number":"1","header":"\u003cdiv class\u003d\"qustion\"\u003e\u003cdiv class\u003d\"field-number\"\u003e  1 \u003c/div\u003e \u003cdiv class\u003d\"field-image\"\u003e  \u003cimg src\u003d\"!image_source!\" alt\u003d\"\"\u003e \u003c/div\u003e \u003cdiv class\u003d\"field-audio\"\u003e   \u003c/div\u003e \u003cdiv class\u003d\"text-center field-subject ans-hide\"\u003e  \u003cp class\u003d\"pinyin\"\u003e妈妈不在家，明明像个小绅士，把阿姨迎进门，跑到桌子前，费力地踮起脚尖，倒了一大杯凉茶，郑重地捧到阿姨面前。阿姨别提多感动了，接过凉茶，瞬间，暑气已经消散了一半。\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e","body":[{"number":"1","value":{"A":"阿姨特别喜欢孩子","B":"阿姨去明明家做客","C":"明明很喜欢喝凉茶","D":"明明自己喝茶自己倒"}}],"category":"NGHE"},{"type":"3","number":"2","header":"\u003cdiv class\u003d\"qustion\"\u003e\u003cdiv class\u003d\"field-number\"\u003e  1 \u003c/div\u003e \u003cdiv class\u003d\"field-image\"\u003e  \u003cimg src\u003d\"!image_source!\" alt\u003d\"\"\u003e \u003c/div\u003e \u003cdiv class\u003d\"field-audio\"\u003e  \u003caudio controls\u003d\"\" controlsList\u003d\"nodownload\"\u003e \r\n  \u003csource src\u003d\"http://localhost:8081/audios/BT/6/01 - Giáo trình chuẩn HSK 6 - SBT - question 1.mp3\" type\u003d\"audio/mpeg\"\u003e Your browser does not support the audio element. \r\n \u003c/audio\u003e \u003cdiv class\u003d\"btn-slide\"\u003e   \u003cdiv class\u003d\"btn\" style\u003d\"    background-color: inherit;    padding-top: 0px;    \"\u003e \u003cspan onclick\u003d\"previous(this)\" type\u003d\"button\"\u003e\u003ci class\u003d\"fa fa-backward\" style\u003d\"    color: black;\"\u003e\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/span\u003e   \u003c/div\u003e   \u003cdiv class\u003d\"btn\" style\u003d\"    background-color: inherit;    padding-right: 30px;    padding-top: 0px;    padding-bottom: 10px;    padding-left: 30px;    \"\u003e \u003cspan onclick\u003d\"next(this)\" type\u003d\"button\"\u003e\u003ci class\u003d\"fa fa-forward\" style\u003d\"    color: black;\"\u003e\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/span\u003e   \u003c/div\u003e  \u003c/div\u003e  \u003cbr\u